{
  "stem": "7094.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My grandmother and the two unmarried, my uncle and aunt with her, and my married aunt with a family moved to Lvov and they lived there incognito.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't have-- they were not hiding Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were hiding the fact that they were well off, they were rich, because one of my uncle who was in Lvov, a very well-known personality and politically, a [NON-ENGLISH] in Lvov, he was taken to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he died without we knowing where he was, because he was considered to be the bourgeoisie.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also he represented a [NON-ENGLISH], so politically, and he was arrested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The family was then in hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there wasn't this pressure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You cannot compare-- I mean, at that time, part of my father's family who moved from the Polish part-- the German part of Poland to this, there was in January, I think '41, there was the Russian have taken all the refugees, knocked at the door, put them on the train, taken them to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, it was a major tragedy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can imagine Siberia, the images we had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were mostly refugees from-- from Germany, you know, who came to here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they just didn't consider anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were politically suspect for them and they didn't consider whether Jews or not Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were taken on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this part of the family survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, this is my father's two sisters who with part of the family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One sister whose family was broken, they survived in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then what are their names?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Friedman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I met them after the war, because we used to send them parcels.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted-- I knew that they were alive, and so I wanted to make contact.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
